    // https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/1290 is solved

        ConfigMaskDummy0,
        ConfigMarketTypeIsStrikedMask, // = 1
        ConfigMaskDummy2,
        ConfigMaskDummy3,

    enum SettlementType {
        FINAL, // = 0
        PRELIMINARY_FIRST // = 1

    enum MarketInterval {
        NONE, // = 0

        MONTHLY, // = 3

        DAILY, // = 5
        HOURLY, // = 6
        SHORT_TERM // = 7
    }
